<% layout('/boilerCode/boilerCode') -%>

    <body>
        <div class="container">
            <div class="about-header">

                <h1>About Spark and Scribe</h1>
                <p style="text-align: center; font-style: italic; color: var(--color-primary-pink);">
                    "From sparks of thought to words that shine."
                </p>
                <p>
                    Spark and Scribe is a dynamic platform dedicated to cultivating original thought and fostering a
                    community of creative writers, thinkers, and sharers. Our mission is to provide an aesthetic,
                    distraction-free space where your ideas can instantly connect with a global audience.
                </p>


                <h2>Core Features</h2>
                <div class="feature-grid">

                    <div class="feature-item">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-bolt"></i>
                        <h4>Real-Time Publishing</h4>
                        <p>Post your thoughts instantly. As soon as you hit publish, your blog post is live and viewable
                            by the entire community.</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="feature-item">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-user-lock"></i>
                        <h4>Secure Authentication</h4>
                        <p>Easy and secure sign-up and login process. Your profile is protected, ensuring only you can
                            manage your creations.</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="feature-item">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-layer-group"></i>
                        <h4>Elegant Card Layout</h4>
                        <p>All blogs are displayed in a clean, modern card format, making the feed visually appealing
                            and easy to scroll through.</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="feature-item">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-mobile-screen-button"></i>
                        <h4>Fully Responsive Design</h4>
                        <p>Enjoy a flawless viewing and writing experience whether you are on a desktop, tablet, or
                            mobile phone.</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="feature-item">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-palette"></i>
                        <h4>Aesthetic Interface</h4>
                        <p>Our soft pink and neutral color palette provides a calm, beautiful background that is
                            pleasing to the eyes.</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="feature-item">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-magnifying-glass"></i>
                        <h4>Centralized Search</h4>
                        <p>Easily find specific topics, authors, or keywords using the prominent, pill-shaped search bar
                            at the top of the feed.</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="feature-item">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-users"></i>
                        <h4>Community Focus</h4>
                        <p>Read, get inspired, and interact with a diverse set of users, turning solo writing into a
                            communal experience.</p>
                    </div>

                </div>


                <h2>How to Use Spark and Scribe</h2>
                <p>Getting started is quick and intuitive. Follow these simple steps to become a contributing member of
                    our community:</p>
                <ol class="guide-list">
                    <li class="guide-step">
                        <!-- <span class="guide-number">1</span> -->
                        <div class="guide-text">
                            <strong>Sign Up or Log In:</strong> Click the "Sign Up" icon on the sidebar to create your
                            account, or "Log In" if you are already a member.
                        </div>
                    </li>
                    <li class="guide-step">
                        <!-- <span class="guide-number">2</span> -->
                        <div class="guide-text">
                            <strong>Navigate to the Feed:</strong> Click the "Home Feed" or "Full Blog List" icons to
                            view all published content.
                        </div>
                    </li>
                    <li class="guide-step">
                        <!-- <span class="guide-number">3</span> -->
                        <div class="guide-text">
                            <strong>Create a Post:</strong> Once logged in, click the "create blog" (<i
                                class="fa-solid fa-plus"></i>) icon on the sidebar to find the publishing form.
                        </div>
                    </li>
                    <li class="guide-step">
                        <!-- <span class="guide-number">4</span> -->
                        <div class="guide-text">
                            <strong>Publish:</strong> Write your thoughts in the text editor and click the **Post Blog**
                            button. Your content is immediately added to the public feed.
                        </div>
                    </li>
                </ol>


                <h2>Why Choose Spark and Scribe?</h2>
                <ul class="benefits-list ">
                    <li>Instantaneous connection with readers worldwide.</li>
                    <li>Clean design minimizes distraction, allowing you to focus purely on writing and reading.</li>
                    <li>The beautiful, fixed sidebar gives easy access to all essential navigation points at all times.
                    </li>
                    <li>A dedicated community aesthetic ensures a pleasant and inspiring user experience.</li>
                    <li>It's the perfect platform to transform fleeting thoughts into lasting pieces of content.</li>
                </ul>

            </div>
        </div>
    </body>

    </html>